    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p>We will be performing a scheduled infrastructure release on the Analytics Cloud to enhance our release process and overall system performance.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"h_01J5NP4RM3BHH1VKP7A7KGBQYR\">What to Expect:</h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Date</strong>: August 20th, 2024</li>\n\t<li><strong>Downtime</strong>: Up to 1 hour</li>\n\t<li><strong>Maintenance Window</strong>: Between 8:00 AM and 8:00 PM PST</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>During this period, you may encounter brief service interruptions. We apologize for any inconvenience and appreciate your patience as we work to deliver a better experience with Analytics Cloud.</p>"
      },
